OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOvernight rain clearing away in
OL,6,Fthe morning with some haar at first
OL,7,Facross Shetland. Then mainly dry with
OL,8,Fsome hazy sunshine and just the odd
OL,9,Fshower possible. A bit warmer.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FStaying mainly dry through
OL,12,Fthe evening with just the odd shower.
OL,13,FRain becoming more persistent for a
OL,14,Ftime overnight before further dry
OL,15,Fspells and a few showers.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FIt will be mainly dry and
OL,18,Fmild with variable cloud and some
OL,19,Fbright or sunny spells, but the chance
OL,20,Fof the odd light shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
